1. Summary: Bug1: Field E-mail: Local part accepts more than 64 characters.
Severity: Average.
Steps:
1. go to https://en.belavia.by/leader/registration/
2. Contact Information, field E-mail.
3. Input Local part more than 64 characters.

Actual result: Local part accepts more than 64 characters.
Expected result: the field is highlighted in red (according to a list of valid and invalid examples of emails, according to RFC 2822).
Attachements: screenshot: https://github.com/Volha2407/Defects/blob/main/Bug1.png
Environment: Windows 10 32-bit Chrome 90.0



2. Summary: Bug2: Field Пасажыры: displays incorrect word form while choosing 3 passengers.
Severity: Minor.
Steps:
1. Go to https://dc-booking.belavia.by/
2. In the drop-down list of languages, select Беларуская.
3. Tab Пошук, radio button Туда и зваротна, field Пасажыры.
4. In the drop-down list choose Дарослы and other passengers to make 3 passengers at all.

Actual result: the field Пасажыры displays 3 Пасажыра.
Expected result: the field Пасажыры displays 3 Пасажыры.

note:
When selecting 4 passengers, the same error occurs.

Attachements: screenshot: https://github.com/Volha2407/Defects/blob/main/Bug2.png
Environment: Windows 10 32-bit Chrome 90.0


3. Summary: Bug3: Field Passengers: displays 2 passengers (1 Adult, 1 Infant), while choosing 1 Adult and 2 Infants.
Severity: Average.
Steps:
1. Go to https://dc-booking.belavia.by/
2. Tab Search, radio button Return, field Passengers.
3. In the drop-down list choose 1 Adult and 2 Infants.

Actual result: the field Passengers displays 2 passengers (1 Adult, 1 Infant).
Expected result: the field Пасажыры displays 3 passengers (1 Adult, 2 Infans).

note:
When selecting 2/3/4/5 adults, you can choose no more than 2/3/4/5 infants

Attachements: screenshot: https://github.com/Volha2407/Defects/blob/main/Bug3.png
Environment: Windows 10 32-bit Chrome 90.0


4. Summary: Bug4: Drop-down list Гости: displays 21 Взрослых, while choosing 21 adults.
Severity: Minor.
Steps:
1. Go to https://belavia.by/
2. In the drop-down list of languages, select Русский.
2. Tab Отели, drop-down list Гости.
3. Choose 21 adults.
4. Note that the word form is incorrect.

Actual result: drop-down list Гости displays 21 Взрослых.
Expected result: drop-down list Гости displays 21 Взрослый.

Attachements: screenshot: https://github.com/Volha2407/Defects/blob/main/Bug4.png
Environment: Windows 10 32-bit Chrome 90.0


5. Summary: Bug5: Information Office: link support@belavia.by doesn't open the page of web-site, while pushing.
Severity: minor.
Steps:
1. Go to https://belavia.by/
2. Go to Information Office.
3. Push the link support@belavia.by.

Actual result: link support@belavia.by doesn't open the page of web-site.
Expected result: go to the page by following the link support@belavia.by.

Attachements: screenshot: 
Environment: Windows 10 32-bit Chrome 90.0
